	<Title>
		Phentermine for weight loss: Can it help?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Phentermine, a prescription medication, can help with weight loss when combined with diet and exercise.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Is phentermine a good option for weight loss?
	</Question>
